{"type": "article", "id": 30551, "title": "多功能毯子", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803231357TCf3cveqMtLiakFo.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>无论是去户外探险还是参加音乐节，毯子都是必不可少的装备，来自美国盐湖城的设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.coalatree.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coalatree</a> 发现普通的毯子并不能一次性满足人们出行时的各种需求，为此他们曾经推出过一款多功能毯子 Kachula，今天要介绍的 V2 就是它的迭代产品。最新款由防水防风的面料制成，采用了双面拉链的设计。它既可以变成一个枕头供人小憩，也可以当作兜帽穿在身上遮风挡雨。不使用的时候只要折叠成小袋塞进包里即可，携带起来非常方便。Kachula 这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/coalatree/kachula-20-the-packable-multi-use-adventure-blanke\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 50 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803231415bxEiJ3thYMmfW1QP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032314159boMWUfgShtA8TB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803231415dSAecbIqnmfwNG92.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803231415E6FqOIQc3M4gPfDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}